node.text: You’re GENUINELY one of the most amazing people I have ever come to know in my life, our knowing each other hasn’t been long but the love and genuine care you’ve shown to me and I guarantee others is nothing to go unnoticed. Your poems are beautiful. Keep it up Taylor! Love you to bits! 💙
@branditbh Aw love you lots! Thank you so much 😭💕

Thank you thank you thank you ✨
P.S. I’ve never put my poetry out into the world like this so I’m —> 🙈😬
.

@shain_aa_ Thank you! ❤️

I love this ❤️ I’ve watched all your videos and your story is a sad one, but filled with strength! And perseverance! And most importantly it’s not over, it’s a new chapter in your life and we’re all here with you 🦋
@dmdonster Oh gosh, I know what you mean. I’m glad they escaped!

My daughter told me about you after you showed up in her recommendations on her YouTube channel! I watch a lot of YouTubers and you totally drew me in! I must have watched like 6 videos in a row 😂 On my mom’s side of the family, we had Jws and I’m glad they all got out years ago but I would always feel bad for my cousins when I was a kid. They were well.. different. I didn’t see pure happiness in them. But anyway, I don’t mean to ramble on and I just want to say you are amazing!!! I love your art, poems, honestly, bravery and very raw videos! You are going to leave a big mark in this world and it’s going to be a good one! Peace ✌🏻 and keep doing what you’re doing!
@marieshepard I’m so sorry. I know it takes a long time to be comfortable with affection again. I still work on that with my husband. I’m proud of you!
@taylor.bjorndahl We have been working on it for 11yrs I’m lucky to have a husband that is understanding. I’m very proud of you as well!!

You are completely amazing! You should proud if everything you have Accomplished. And how fair you have come. I just watched everyone of your videos in a day. Your not along. I had a an abusive dad physically and I am just now overcoming the pain I no longer flinch when my husband tries to touch me when I’m not paying attention.
I love this! 😍🙏🏼You’re amazing and such an inspiration to us! 🥰🥰 looking forward to more 🤗
@dkfollows 💖
@dkfollows ❤️❤️❤️

I've just started watching your videos. I was raised Christian, not even JW, but I can relate to so much you're saying and you are so brave to share all of this. It made me so happy that you and your husband were able to get out of this together, you both deserve to be so loved, I'm glad you have each other. I'm sure you're going to meet so much more people who feel the same. The "world" is actually kind of a nice place, with a lot of lovely (far less judgemental) people in it. It will probably take some time to adjust and especially heal, in your new situation, but I feel like your videos and poetry are definitely gonna help you with that. I wish you all the best!
You’re amazing 💖

Amazing Taylor,  you are very talented.. After everything you've been through, I am so happy that you are now able to live a life where your beautiful personality and soul can shine out into the world where it can be finally appreciated.. Keep your strength, doing what you're doing & you will go far! 🤗🌍🌻🌈💗x

This is amazing & heartfelt. I've been watching all your videos since you statred your channel and they have touched me deeply. You are truly an inspiration and a beautiful human being. Much positive vibes to you. 🙌❤️🌟
Taylor, you are such an amazing being! Hope U are doing well and allways will :)
You are so gifted, talented.  Lyrical.  I am almost 70 (looking forward to it!), a mom and granny, and will adopt you today if you want it.  to
Love this!!!!
@traceykhouston_music Awesome! I’m backed up on emails, I’ll try to reply asap 🥰
Good stuff Taylor.  I sent you an email a few days ago (to your email address).
Beautiful 😭😍
Super powerful👏🏼 great job!!!
Very beautiful!❤️
So beautiful! 😢 Thank you for sharing!! Keep it coming!
Indeed it is not your fault, and for sure I am one who is here for you ✌🏽. I’m so glad you can be moved to write such words and have them be true ✊🏽💙
Love you sis and bro. You are awesome
@thunderclutz That makes me so happy to hear! 😭👏🏻 Proud of you 💕

This is beautiful. Thank you so much for everything Taylor. I just discovered you a few days ago and just finished all your videos today. You truly inspired me to get up and make my life better, and my mind clearer, so thank you for that.

This is absolutely beautiful! Wonderful words. 💖 I have watched your story and was in shock at the horrors you have endured. You are an amazing human! You are helping so many just by sharing your story. 🌺
@branditbh Aw love you lots! Thank you so much 😭💕

You’re GENUINELY one of the most amazing people I have ever come to know in my life, our knowing each other hasn’t been long but the love and genuine care you’ve shown to me and I guarantee others is nothing to go unnoticed. Your poems are beautiful. Keep it up Taylor! Love you to bits! 💙
